Description: A backpack isn’t just a bag. It’s a cache, a case, a mobile base of sorts. And it is a reflection of the care you’ve put into selecting the ideal loadout of items to keep on you. Product Description: Ergonomic Contoured ShapeWith a slim, sleek and compact design you will love how this backpack can look small even with a spacious storage!Fits Your LaptopTake your gadgets with you anywhere with this backpack, it has got allotted storage space that fits a laptop of upto 15.6 inches.Strong and LightweightDesigned with great quality materials that are waterproof, tough and durable, it is also lightweight and easy to maintain.Padded Back StrapsThe back straps are padded to give the user maximum support and it made with anti-sweat fabric, giving you the comfort throughout the day.Spacious StorageFeaturing 2 compartments, the main compartment and a front compartment to store smaller objects/pens/thin notebooks etc. It also includes a laptop sleeve with a Velcro strap for safety.Back SupportIt won’t feel uneasy to carry heavy things for a longer time with this bag as it has a cushioned back support that distributes weight evenly between your shoulders and back.A Bag for any weatherBe it those stormy rainy season, scorching heat, or freezing winters, this bag can endure as it is crafted, designed and made with quality and tough materials.
